Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Floods in California
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xpr4
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 9 Mar 1986
Homes and crops wiped out after massive flooding leaves northern California under water. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less